\n之後就慢慢慢慢好番左 啲指紋都全部生番哂出嚟<br />\n<br />\n我覺得最緊要係 你平時洗手盡量唔好用清潔劑<br />\n只用清水 可以每晚訓前用一次温和既洗手液洗手<br />\n依家疫情勁左 我都係一日最多用2-3次溫和洗手液<br />\n唔知你用咩沖涼液 我隻手沖涼都唔可以掂滴露沖涼液<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得搽多啲cream保濕<br />\n呢樣好緊要"},{"pid":"0a78e81f9fc7a1093c911cdffb2f765c450d311c","tid":2161947,"uid":368287,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T18:27:00.000Z","msg":"唔好亂用類固醇 濕疹係身體免疫系統失調 身體不停自己打緊自己 係長期問題 你用類只係短期有用 但皮膚變薄 身體對類耐受程度提升 愈用愈高劑量 never end.<br />\n我建議你由supplement 同飲食習慣開始 <br />\n先搞好腸道健康 同低醣原型飲食<br />\n基本上無得醫 係睇下點相處既啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0989f1acec1bd7204cf4de61dbb91daad9757178","tid":2161947,"uid":333360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T20:13:21.000Z","msg":"要自律食清啲，希望樓主唔係類固醇上癮，好難斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1021088b159fbd490786856150e5ec00794b00c","tid":2161947,"uid":302733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T21:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468b4adea9f40a1030653cb5559605ae1fcfb8bf","tid":2161947,"uid":368824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T16:56:07.000Z","msg":"唔一定，我自己就冇搽藥，驚類固醇上癮。之前有一排隻手都好嚴重，開始左食益生菌同中藥，同試左一隻叫敘利亞梘嘅番梘沖涼洗手，之後就開始好轉。不過每個人唔同，未必個個啱同樣方法。最好就係戒口，因為濕疹有機會係延遲性過敏反應，最好都係避開啲過敏源。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cErBAT8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcErBAT8.png&h=3686bfe5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BX12wsz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBX12wsz.png&h=c4dc0f99&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eS3z60V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeS3z60V.jpg&h=4e2f284c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3W66dFW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3W66dFW.jpg&h=e75cd27d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f42b230b795c7ba71728ac686335a18f8cbeadb","tid":2161947,"uid":171139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:44:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be0c0cc75f606ae48ff1de1bc8d0db4f695f521e","tid":2161947,"uid":265269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe3da6aba67366e33b4dfd65c840d999074729bd","tid":2161947,"uid":104834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:04:15.000Z","msg":"我由細到大都有，近年壓力大出返<br />\n細個睇西醫搽太多類固醇，皮膚變得好薄<br />\n不過近年濕疹，轉工之後好好多，可能真係有影響<br />\n另外一定要早訓，生活習慣好緊要<br />\n仲有飲食都有改變，減奶減糖，唔食咁多有湯嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n我用咗手工藥膏之後，加埋身體好咗，慢慢好緊<br />\n不過會喺個身度周圍走，所以都要搽cream、照顧多啲<br />\n睇張圖望落似係汗皰疹，可以試下搽紫黃膏、龍血濕疹膏<br />\n搽完涼浸浸、那那地，即刻唔痕，感覺會舒服好多"},{"pid":"e3d3fad8e396567885d26467866156e39550b3ba","tid":2161947,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"468b4adea9f40a1030653cb5559605ae1fcfb8bf","tid":2161947,"uid":368824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T16:56:07.000Z","msg":"唔一定，我自己就冇搽藥，驚類固醇上癮。之前有一排隻手都好嚴重，開始左食益生菌同中藥，同試左一隻叫敘利亞梘嘅番梘沖涼洗手，之後就開始好轉。不過每個人唔同，未必個個啱同樣方法。最好就係戒口，因為濕疹有機會係延遲性過敏反應，最好都係避開啲過敏源。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cErBAT8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcErBAT8.png&h=3686bfe5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BX12wsz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBX12wsz.png&h=c4dc0f99&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eS3z60V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeS3z60V.jpg&h=4e2f284c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3W66dFW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3W66dFW.jpg&h=e75cd27d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:42:41.000Z","msg":"仲以為係我隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb997fb8cdc08f4669a